headline: Why AbbVie (ABBV) Shares Are Falling Today
summary: Shares of pharmaceutical company AbbVie (NYSE:ABBV) fell 3.9% in the afternoon session after the company reported third-quarter results that were overshadowed by a steep drop in profitability and a reduced earnings forecast for the full year.
